â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ai/               # AI service integrations
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ api/              # API routes
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ database/         # Prisma schema
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ payments/         # Stripe integration
